Goal (Base Class)
Purpose:  
Represents a general goal in the Eternal Quest system. Provides shared structure and behavior for all goal types.

Responsibilities:

Store the name, description, and base point value

Track completion status

Provide a common interface for recording progress

Provide a common interface for displaying goal status

Provide a common interface for saving/loading goal data

