---------------------------------------------------------
ChecklistGoal
Purpose:  
A goal that must be completed a certain number of times. Awards points each time, plus a bonus when fully completed.

Responsibilities:

Inherit from Goal

Track how many times it has been completed

Award base points each time

Award bonus points when target count is reached

Mark itself complete when finished

