GoalManager_RP
Purpose:  
Manages all goals, user score, saving/loading, and recording events.

Responsibilities:

Store a list of goals

Store the user’s total score

Add new goals

Display goals

Record goal completion

Save goals to a file

Load goals from a file

Provide gamification features (levels, bonuses, etc.)

